:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>أَسۡفَلَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> مِنكُمۡۚ وَلَوۡ تَوَاعَدتُّمۡ لَٱخۡتَلَفۡتُمۡ فِي </div><div>ٱلۡمِيعَٰدِ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَلَٰكِن</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> لِّيَقۡضِيَ ٱللَّهُ أَمۡرٗا كَانَ مَفۡعُولٗا لِّيَهۡلِكَ </div><div>مَنۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>هَلَكَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> عَنۢ بَيِّنَةٖ وَيَحۡيَىٰ مَنۡ حَيَّ عَنۢ بَيِّنَةٖۗ وَإِنَّ </div><div>ٱللَّهَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>لَسَمِيعٌ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> عَلِيمٌ ٤٢ إِذۡ يُرِيكَهُمُ ٱللَّهُ فِي مَنَامِكَ </div><div>قَلِيلٗاۖ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَلَوۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> أَرَىٰكَهُمۡ كَثِيرٗا <a data-content='لجُبنتُم عن القتال وهبتموه' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>لَّفَشِلۡتُمۡ</a> وَلَتَنَٰزَعۡتُمۡ فِي </div><div>ٱلۡأَمۡرِ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَلَٰكِنَّ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱللَّهَ سَلَّمَۚ إِنَّهُۥ عَلِيمُۢ بِذَاتِ ٱلصُّدُورِ ٤٣ </div><div>وَإِذۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>يُرِيكُمُوهُمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> إِذِ ٱلۡتَقَيۡتُمۡ فِيٓ أَعۡيُنِكُمۡ قَلِيلٗا </div><div>وَيُقَلِّلُكُمۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>فِيٓ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> أَعۡيُنِهِمۡ لِيَقۡضِيَ ٱللَّهُ أَمۡرٗا كَانَ مَفۡع